<section class="section bg-sage relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grain opacity-[0.03]" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-ivory/30 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-ivory/30 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  
  <div class="container-elegant relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 border border-ivory/25 rounded-full backdrop-blur-sm bg-ivory/5">
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-ivory opacity-50"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-ivory"></span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-ivory/90">Primera consulta sin compromiso</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl text-ivory leading-tight mb-6">
        Da el primer paso hacia tu <span class="italic font-light">bienestar</span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg text-ivory/75 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        No tienes que recorrer este camino en soledad. Reserva una sesión y descubre cómo la terapia puede ayudarte.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-light">
          <span>Solicitar cita ahora</span>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17.25 8.75L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.25M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        
        <a href="tel:+34661471971" class="btn btn-ghost">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" />
          </svg>
          <span>661 471 971</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-ivory/10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-ivory/60">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ivory/40" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          <span>Respuesta en 24h</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-ivory/60">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ivory/40" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" />
